{"componentChunkName":"component---src-template-blog-post-template-js","path":"/blog/about-ad-blocker-and-tracker-protection/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<p>分享我了解到的广告拦截方案，更准确地说是内容拦截方案，因为很多时候需要拦截的不仅仅是广告，还有跟踪器、影响体验的一些非广告页面元素等等，例如下面这张图片，是不是有点恐怖呢：</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"color: grey; font-size: 0.8rem; text-align: center; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0; border: 1px solid #eee\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 65.14285714285714%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/b9f473939a4114e1d30a6044adc1a3b2/c54d4/annoy-ads.webp 175w,\n/static/b9f473939a4114e1d30a6044adc1a3b2/a3432/annoy-ads.webp 350w,\n/static/b9f473939a4114e1d30a6044adc1a3b2/426ac/annoy-ads.webp 700w,\n/static/b9f473939a4114e1d30a6044adc1a3b2/c139f/annoy-ads.webp 1050w,\n/static/b9f473939a4114e1d30a6044adc1a3b2/af3f0/annoy-ads.webp 1280w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/b9f473939a4114e1d30a6044adc1a3b2/e52aa/annoy-ads.jpg 175w,\n/static/b9f473939a4114e1d30a6044adc1a3b2/70ebb/annoy-ads.jpg 350w,\n/static/b9f473939a4114e1d30a6044adc1a3b2/29d31/annoy-ads.jpg 700w,\n/static/b9f473939a4114e1d30a6044adc1a3b2/9ecec/annoy-ads.jpg 1050w,\n/static/b9f473939a4114e1d30a6044adc1a3b2/eea4a/annoy-ads.jpg 1280w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/b9f473939a4114e1d30a6044adc1a3b2/29d31/annoy-ads.jpg\"\n          alt=\"各种令人讨厌的页面元素\"\n          title=\"各种令人讨厌的页面元素\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">各种令人讨厌的页面元素</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>电脑-浏览器内置的拦截工具</h2>\n<p>例如微软 Edge 内置了跟踪防护，可以屏蔽广告跟踪器，跟踪器其实就是一段代码，例如 Google Analytics.js。跟踪器能收集用户或设备的信息，跟踪你访问过哪些网站等，广告主于是能根据你的浏览行为对你投放广告。有时候我们在京东看了一双鞋，打开其他网站马上就能看到这双鞋的广告。</p>\n<p>Firefox、Safari 也内置跟踪器防护功能；但是 Chrome 没有。至于广告屏蔽，以上浏览器都没有内置。</p>\n<p>下图是被 Edge 内置的跟踪防护功能阻止的爱奇艺网站的跟踪器：</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"color: grey; font-size: 0.8rem; text-align: center; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0; border: 1px solid #eee\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 65.14285714285714%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/db22c80fe87fe8841fcd1a650dc4e35d/c54d4/edge-block-tracker.webp 175w,\n/static/db22c80fe87fe8841fcd1a650dc4e35d/a3432/edge-block-tracker.webp 350w,\n/static/db22c80fe87fe8841fcd1a650dc4e35d/426ac/edge-block-tracker.webp 700w,\n/static/db22c80fe87fe8841fcd1a650dc4e35d/3f436/edge-block-tracker.webp 708w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/db22c80fe87fe8841fcd1a650dc4e35d/e52aa/edge-block-tracker.jpg 175w,\n/static/db22c80fe87fe8841fcd1a650dc4e35d/70ebb/edge-block-tracker.jpg 350w,\n/static/db22c80fe87fe8841fcd1a650dc4e35d/29d31/edge-block-tracker.jpg 700w,\n/static/db22c80fe87fe8841fcd1a650dc4e35d/2acc6/edge-block-tracker.jpg 708w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/db22c80fe87fe8841fcd1a650dc4e35d/29d31/edge-block-tracker.jpg\"\n          alt=\"爱奇艺\"\n          title=\"爱奇艺\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">爱奇艺</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>电脑-浏览器插件</h2>\n<p>AdGuard、Adblock 、Adblock Plus、uBlock Origin 等广告拦截插件，除了可以阻止跟踪器，还可以屏蔽广告、屏蔽一些虽然不是广告但令人讨厌的弹窗等页面元素。这四款工具效果各异，这里不评价。</p>\n<p>下图是淘宝网站被屏蔽的内容，应该不止广告，看来还省了很多流量。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"color: grey; font-size: 0.8rem; text-align: center; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0; border: 1px solid #eee\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 96%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/c57ce147614891856a56aecbfd873e45/c54d4/taobao.webp 175w,\n/static/c57ce147614891856a56aecbfd873e45/a3432/taobao.webp 350w,\n/static/c57ce147614891856a56aecbfd873e45/426ac/taobao.webp 700w,\n/static/c57ce147614891856a56aecbfd873e45/a5d4d/taobao.webp 1000w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/c57ce147614891856a56aecbfd873e45/e52aa/taobao.jpg 175w,\n/static/c57ce147614891856a56aecbfd873e45/70ebb/taobao.jpg 350w,\n/static/c57ce147614891856a56aecbfd873e45/29d31/taobao.jpg 700w,\n/static/c57ce147614891856a56aecbfd873e45/a2510/taobao.jpg 1000w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/c57ce147614891856a56aecbfd873e45/29d31/taobao.jpg\"\n          alt=\"淘宝\"\n          title=\"淘宝\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">淘宝</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>电脑-广告屏蔽软件</h2>\n<p>浏览器插件只能用于浏览器内，有一些内容拦截工具还有桌面版应用，例如 AdGuard 等，它们支持系统级的广告过滤，可过滤浏览器和其他应用的广告，不过可能收费。</p>\n<p>浏览器插件必须遵守浏览器的规则，不见得所有浏览器都希望你屏蔽广告，例如 Chrome 应该不希望你拦截 Google 的广告，而系统级别的内容拦截软件可以摆脱这些限制。</p>\n<h2>手机-浏览器插件</h2>\n<p>手机版的 Chrome 不能屏蔽广告；Edge 内置了 Adblock Plus 用于屏蔽广告，需手动开启，Edge 和电脑版一样，支持阻止跟踪器；Safari 本身支持阻止跨域跟踪但不支持屏蔽广告，不过可通过第三方内容拦截器屏蔽广告；Firefox 能阻止跟踪。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"color: grey; font-size: 0.8rem; text-align: center; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0; border: 1px solid #eee\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 107.42857142857143%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/ad70cac1ed68af36ee251321a17645ed/c54d4/edge-safari-setting.webp 175w,\n/static/ad70cac1ed68af36ee251321a17645ed/a3432/edge-safari-setting.webp 350w,\n/static/ad70cac1ed68af36ee251321a17645ed/426ac/edge-safari-setting.webp 700w,\n/static/ad70cac1ed68af36ee251321a17645ed/c139f/edge-safari-setting.webp 1050w,\n/static/ad70cac1ed68af36ee251321a17645ed/af3f0/edge-safari-setting.webp 1280w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/ad70cac1ed68af36ee251321a17645ed/e52aa/edge-safari-setting.jpg 175w,\n/static/ad70cac1ed68af36ee251321a17645ed/70ebb/edge-safari-setting.jpg 350w,\n/static/ad70cac1ed68af36ee251321a17645ed/29d31/edge-safari-setting.jpg 700w,\n/static/ad70cac1ed68af36ee251321a17645ed/9ecec/edge-safari-setting.jpg 1050w,\n/static/ad70cac1ed68af36ee251321a17645ed/eea4a/edge-safari-setting.jpg 1280w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/ad70cac1ed68af36ee251321a17645ed/29d31/edge-safari-setting.jpg\"\n          alt=\"safari 和 edge\"\n          title=\"safari 和 edge\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">safari 和 edge</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>手机-内容拦截应用</h2>\n<p>AdGuard 有 iOS 和 Android 版，但需要付费才能拦截其他应用的广告，否则只能作用于浏览器；Adblock Plus、Adblock 在 iOS 和 Android 都没有全局拦截功能，要不就是作为浏览器插件存在，要不就是开发一个主打广告拦截的浏览器；uBlock Origin 不支持手机。</p>\n<p>下图是 Adblock Plus、Adblock 针对三星手机浏览器的插件截图：</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"color: grey; font-size: 0.8rem; text-align: center; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0; border: 1px solid #eee\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 41.142857142857146%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/fec2cf0218d538ca679bc8522b58dfea/c54d4/adblock.webp 175w,\n/static/fec2cf0218d538ca679bc8522b58dfea/a3432/adblock.webp 350w,\n/static/fec2cf0218d538ca679bc8522b58dfea/426ac/adblock.webp 700w,\n/static/fec2cf0218d538ca679bc8522b58dfea/c139f/adblock.webp 1050w,\n/static/fec2cf0218d538ca679bc8522b58dfea/af3f0/adblock.webp 1280w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/fec2cf0218d538ca679bc8522b58dfea/e52aa/adblock.jpg 175w,\n/static/fec2cf0218d538ca679bc8522b58dfea/70ebb/adblock.jpg 350w,\n/static/fec2cf0218d538ca679bc8522b58dfea/29d31/adblock.jpg 700w,\n/static/fec2cf0218d538ca679bc8522b58dfea/9ecec/adblock.jpg 1050w,\n/static/fec2cf0218d538ca679bc8522b58dfea/eea4a/adblock.jpg 1280w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/fec2cf0218d538ca679bc8522b58dfea/29d31/adblock.jpg\"\n          alt=\"AdBlock\"\n          title=\"AdBlock\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">AdBlock</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>DNS 或 host</h2>\n<p>Android 平台有一款叫 AdAway 的广告拦截应用，通过修改 host 阻止广告请求，已经开发了很多年，但因为需要 root，不太流行。DNS 拦截和改 host 拦截原理差不多，我用过的有 nextDNS，可以拦截浏览器和应用中的广告，但可能影响国内网站访问速度，例如在浏览器打开百度慢很多。DNS 方案甚至可以用在路由器，这样所有连接到这个网络的设备都可以过滤广告，只是我还没找到好用的广告过滤DNS。</p>\n<p>GitHub 有一个叫 pi-hole 的开源项目，可以用树莓派自建 DNS 拦截服务。</p>\n<p>下图是 nextDNS 的数据统计面板：</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"color: grey; font-size: 0.8rem; text-align: center; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0; border: 1px solid #eee\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.285714285714285%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/56e65c3867c926bb4829b17321622d44/c54d4/nextDNS.webp 175w,\n/static/56e65c3867c926bb4829b17321622d44/a3432/nextDNS.webp 350w,\n/static/56e65c3867c926bb4829b17321622d44/426ac/nextDNS.webp 700w,\n/static/56e65c3867c926bb4829b17321622d44/c139f/nextDNS.webp 1050w,\n/static/56e65c3867c926bb4829b17321622d44/df6ba/nextDNS.webp 1156w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/56e65c3867c926bb4829b17321622d44/e52aa/nextDNS.jpg 175w,\n/static/56e65c3867c926bb4829b17321622d44/70ebb/nextDNS.jpg 350w,\n/static/56e65c3867c926bb4829b17321622d44/29d31/nextDNS.jpg 700w,\n/static/56e65c3867c926bb4829b17321622d44/9ecec/nextDNS.jpg 1050w,\n/static/56e65c3867c926bb4829b17321622d44/7f09e/nextDNS.jpg 1156w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/56e65c3867c926bb4829b17321622d44/29d31/nextDNS.jpg\"\n          alt=\"nextDNS\"\n          title=\"nextDNS\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">nextDNS</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>关于屏蔽规则</h2>\n<p>上面提到的所有内容拦截工具都离不开 EasyList 这个开源项目，EasyList 针对不同的用户需求维护了众多内容拦截规则，有些开发者例如 AdGuard 还会维护自己的规则，他们称之为过滤器，在 GitHub 还能找到很多由网友个人维护的过滤列表。</p>\n<p>EasyList 的部分过滤规则如下：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>EasyList：这是主要的过滤器，Removes most adverts from international webpages；</li>\n<li>EasyPrivacy：作为 EasyList 主过滤器的补充，阻止各种跟踪器；</li>\n<li>EasyList Cookie List：移除网站的 Cookies 弹窗提示；</li>\n<li>Fanboy's Social Blocking List：移除页面上的社交分享按钮；</li>\n<li>Fanboy's Annoyance List：包含了 EasyList Cookie List、Fanboy's Social Blocking List，如果你用了这个规则，上面两个就不需要了。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>其他 EasyList 过滤规则可能是以上规则的补充或变体，或根据某些要求制定的：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>针对不同国家或地区的过滤器，例如 EasyList China，由 John、Li 两位作者维护，适合中国用户使用；</li>\n<li>EasyPrivacy Tracking Protection List：专门为 IE9 准备的规则；</li>\n<li>还有很多为其他国家或语言准备的过滤规则。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>EasyList 里面有很多以 <a href=\"https://github.com/ryanbr/\">Fanboy</a> 开头的列表，这是因为以前 Fanboy 过滤规则是独立的，它甚至有自己的<a href=\"https://fanboy.co.nz/filters.html\">官网</a>。2013 年 5 月 Fanboy 和 EasyList 整合在一起维护，其中 Fanboy's Tracking List 并入了 EasyPrivacy。大概也是那段时间，Fanboy's Social Blocking List 从 Fanboy's Annoyance List 分离出来独立作为一个新规则。</p>\n<h2>反广告屏蔽</h2>\n<p>我曾经是广告屏蔽插件的忠实用户，Adblock 、Adblock Plus、uBlock Origin 这些浏览器插件我都用过，后来好像是迫于多种压力，这些插件屏蔽广告的做法不那么激进了，允许展示 “可接受广告”，于是屏蔽效果开始下降。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"color: grey; font-size: 0.8rem; text-align: center; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0; border: 1px solid #eee\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.85714285714286%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/1deb2819c6158d6b3b7179f3c41233e3/c54d4/acceptable-ads.webp 175w,\n/static/1deb2819c6158d6b3b7179f3c41233e3/a3432/acceptable-ads.webp 350w,\n/static/1deb2819c6158d6b3b7179f3c41233e3/426ac/acceptable-ads.webp 700w,\n/static/1deb2819c6158d6b3b7179f3c41233e3/a5d4d/acceptable-ads.webp 1000w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/1deb2819c6158d6b3b7179f3c41233e3/e52aa/acceptable-ads.jpg 175w,\n/static/1deb2819c6158d6b3b7179f3c41233e3/70ebb/acceptable-ads.jpg 350w,\n/static/1deb2819c6158d6b3b7179f3c41233e3/29d31/acceptable-ads.jpg 700w,\n/static/1deb2819c6158d6b3b7179f3c41233e3/a2510/acceptable-ads.jpg 1000w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/1deb2819c6158d6b3b7179f3c41233e3/29d31/acceptable-ads.jpg\"\n          alt=\"可接受广告\"\n          title=\"可接受广告\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">可接受广告</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>另一个重要原因是，很多网站也开始采取反广告屏蔽措施，友好一点的就是弹出一个几秒到十几秒后自动消失的提示，提醒你关闭屏蔽功能；粗鲁一点的就完全禁止你浏览网页内容，直到你对它停止屏蔽。这是我不再使用屏蔽插件的主要原因，烦不胜烦，就卸了。</p>\n<p>如果你不知道如何 BlockAdblock，有人甚至免费提供了反广告屏蔽代码，帮助站长快速布署：</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"color: grey; font-size: 0.8rem; text-align: center; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0; border: 1px solid #eee\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 96%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/77640b18ff9e73c29e2c5f17665f1e6e/c54d4/blockadblocker.webp 175w,\n/static/77640b18ff9e73c29e2c5f17665f1e6e/a3432/blockadblocker.webp 350w,\n/static/77640b18ff9e73c29e2c5f17665f1e6e/426ac/blockadblocker.webp 700w,\n/static/77640b18ff9e73c29e2c5f17665f1e6e/42cfc/blockadblocker.webp 781w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/77640b18ff9e73c29e2c5f17665f1e6e/e52aa/blockadblocker.jpg 175w,\n/static/77640b18ff9e73c29e2c5f17665f1e6e/70ebb/blockadblocker.jpg 350w,\n/static/77640b18ff9e73c29e2c5f17665f1e6e/29d31/blockadblocker.jpg 700w,\n/static/77640b18ff9e73c29e2c5f17665f1e6e/1cf11/blockadblocker.jpg 781w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/77640b18ff9e73c29e2c5f17665f1e6e/29d31/blockadblocker.jpg\"\n          alt=\"反广告屏蔽\"\n          title=\"反广告屏蔽\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">反广告屏蔽</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>BlockAdblock 的作者反广告屏蔽的理由是：The free web is important. Free media is important.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"关于手机和电脑的广告拦截、跟踪防护","date":"2020/12/18","slug":"about-ad-blocker-and-tracker-protection","description":null}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"about-ad-blocker-and-tracker-protection"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1518281631"]}